dotfiles for osx

Currently using the following:

* terminal is osx default Terminal
* Terminal theme is Material shell: https://materialshell.carloscuesta.me/
* Font is MesloLGS NG Regular Font (12pt laptop, 24pt iMac): https://github.com/romkatv/powerlevel10k#meslo-nerd-font-patched-for-powerlevel10k
* shell is zsh `.zshrc`
* shell plugins managed with antibody (~/.zsh_plugins.txt): https://getantibody.github.io/install/
* shell prompt is powerlevel10k (see zsh_plugins.txt and .zshrc reference to powerlevel10k. https://github.com/romkatv/powerlevel10k#antibody)
* vim colorscheme is apprentice: https://github.com/romainl/Apprentice
* npm packages are globally installed per `.npmrc`: https://jamesauble.medium.com/install-nvm-on-mac-with-brew-adb921fb92cc
* eslint config uses airbnb style guide
